{"tid":1760783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 政府撥逾960萬賑濟印度水災災民","createTime":"2019-11-28T12:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T13:04:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":39,"dislike":398,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"13d3ab5ff8e221f6b7e00e36eacc58d3180c7c27","tid":1760783,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"政府接納賑災基金諮詢委員會的建議，從賑災基金批出兩項共960萬7千元的撥款，予兩間機構賑濟印度比哈爾邦水災災民。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，印度比哈爾邦水災的受災人數超過2百萬人。兩項撥款分別為510萬8千元予香港仁人家園及449萬9千元予國際培幼會（香港）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495004-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495004-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=eed8b48a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495004-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=626664a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495004-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"63e5597b7e96ca08357e1ba0cb713da9c026eb84","tid":1760783,"uid":103759,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOn9 無下限"},{"pid":"448ca07e32dfe12da681e43e8796fe198356ab00","tid":1760783,"uid":19454,"like":235,"dislike":0,"score":235,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:44:46.000Z","msg":"慈禧：寧贈友邦，不予家奴"},{"pid":"e013d2b3999cccc3b6e968e77fa5a8994bfa3617","tid":1760783,"uid":11148,"like":34,"dislike":8,"score":26,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:45:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩項撥款分別為510萬8千元予香港仁人家園及449萬9千元予國際培幼會（香港）</spa